    "class": "gps-607888784247227290 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=607864187825160759&sectionId=607888784247227290)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggs8jkNaELT_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggs8jkNaELT_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_d7apdhd7apdhd7ap.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-s0U6soG1_text","label":"gg-s0U6soG1_text","default":"<p>So he did something radical. He quit his 20-year position at a major pharmaceutical company.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrhb7v8AsY_text","label":"ggrhb7v8AsY_text","default":"<p>Dr. Marcus Chen teamed up with three trusted colleagues: Dr. Elena Reid (cellular biologist), Dr. Rowan James (longevity researcher), and Dr. Marcus DeShawn (osteologist).</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8pzDZbs5C_text","label":"gg8pzDZbs5C_text","default":"<p>For over 2 years, they tested everything. Studied the Okinawan diet. Researched NAD+. Tested formulation after formulation.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYXdI-yk_g_text","label":"ggYXdI-yk_g_text","default":"<p>There were failures. Dead ends. Ingredients that didn't work.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWWqMTc7aw_text","label":"ggWWqMTc7aw_text","default":"<p>But Dr. Chen's mother was his North Star. He tested every breakthrough on her first.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKekNfr3oa_text","label":"ggKekNfr3oa_text","default":"<p><strong>After 47 failed formulations, something changed... His mother called him crying—not from pain. From joy.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDHHltiLdp_text","label":"ggDHHltiLdp_text","default":"<p><i>\"Last Saturday, little Miko asked me to chase him around the backyard. I actually did it. I jogged. I didn't limp. I didn't hold my breath waiting for pain. I just moved like a normal grandmother.\"</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl4xBQCUfP_text","label":"ggl4xBQCUfP_text","default":"<p>That's when Dr. Chen knew they had it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggq71DIpz19_text","label":"ggq71DIpz19_text","default":"<p><strong>He called it Thryve.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggq_ia6MVLE_text","label":"ggq_ia6MVLE_text","default":"<p>But he also realized something else: His mother wasn't alone. Millions of women were trapped in the same nightmare...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxbYRwfu2E_text","label":"ggxbYRwfu2E_text","default":"<p>Silent disease. No warning. One moment changes everything. Told drugs were their only option, trapped in bodies that felt like they were failing them.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPpVnkxLve_text","label":"ggPpVnkxLve_text","default":"<p><i>Dr. Chen made a decision. He wasn't going to keep this in a lab for the wealthy. He was never going to sell it to Big Pharma so they could mark it up 1,000%.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAMeXQS23C_text","label":"ggAMeXQS23C_text","default":"<p>That's why he named their mission Thirmik, literally meaning \"The Small Healer\" in Ancient Greek. A symbol of resistance against corporate medicine.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggG_xmYDPZT_text","label":"ggG_xmYDPZT_text","default":"<p><strong>He was going to make sure every woman who needed this could actually get it. That's why he spent the last year documenting everything.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggo1mYdaXhX_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggo1mYdaXhX_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_hsp0fwhsp0fwhsp0.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWvn2N22-g_text","label":"ggWvn2N22-g_text","default":"<p>I sat at my kitchen table, reading his research papers. Looking at the actual published studies.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjfdg7aZ06_text","label":"ggjfdg7aZ06_text","default":"<p><strong>Real women. Real results. Published science in peer-reviewed journals.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxGHRLXsSw_text","label":"ggxGHRLXsSw_text","default":"<p>I thought about my next bone scan in six months.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggY03jT1J_N_text","label":"ggY03jT1J_N_text","default":"<p><strong>I thought about my grandmother in that wheelchair.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFvTXY1XMj_text","label":"ggFvTXY1XMj_text","default":"<p>I thought about being too scared to pick up my future grandchildren.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi1bl1QkCJ_text","label":"ggi1bl1QkCJ_text","default":"<p>At some point, I started crying.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQsU4z0Vvo_text","label":"ggQsU4z0Vvo_text","default":"<p>My husband found me sitting there, papers spread across the table.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggq59SEdRoo_text","label":"ggq59SEdRoo_text","default":"<p><i>“What happened?”</i> he asked.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNGprUED0g_text","label":"ggNGprUED0g_text","default":"<p><i><strong>\"I think I finally found an answer,\" I told him. \"I'm just scared to hope again.\"</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmjbk6oDPm_text","label":"ggmjbk6oDPm_text","default":"<p>He put his hand on my shoulder.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYyqjIt5bH_text","label":"ggYyqjIt5bH_text","default":"<p><i>\"Then test it. What do you have to lose?\"</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguSWW5WkqM_text","label":"gguSWW5WkqM_text","default":"<p>He was right.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrdlE_zvpK_text","label":"ggrdlE_zvpK_text","default":"<p><strong>So I gave myself six months, one last try before accepting defeat.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-H1hry-FF_text","label":"gg-H1hry-FF_text","default":"<p><strong>What Happened In The First 2 Months Surprised Me</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9OoveVtS4_text","label":"gg9OoveVtS4_text","default":"<p><strong>I'm not going to lie and say it was instant magic.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJehb3Ac6q_text","label":"ggJehb3Ac6q_text","default":"<p>The first week, I felt... nothing. I almost gave up.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkMRV_xH8L_text","label":"ggkMRV_xH8L_text","default":"<p>But around week 3, I noticed something small.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg57qaWu89q_text","label":"gg57qaWu89q_text","default":"<p><strong>I woke up without my usual morning stiffness.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi3VcyVkmn_text","label":"ggi3VcyVkmn_text","default":"<p>Getting out of bed didn't require the slow, painful roll-and-push routine I'd developed.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSW2DFaGJk_text","label":"ggSW2DFaGJk_text","default":"<p>I could just... stand up. Like a normal person.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHr8lIuHuY_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggHr8lIuHuY_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_urn40purn40purn4.webp"}],
    "blocks": [{"type": "@app"}],
    "locales": {}
